node.text: We wanna go on a vacay too!

< C O N T E S T > 
Fancy a Vacation this June Holiday? 
We visited the beach & the desert! 
How bout you? 
Do you have any destination in mind to create for your family? 
Join us on a Virtual Vacation 
with @August_society !

The TWO best and most creative submissions will receive 
SGD $250 worth of swimwear.
@august_society is a Singapore-based sustainable swimwear brand for the whole family. Ethically produced from top- quality recycled fabrics, our swimsuits feature timeless styles, mix and match, reversible and multi-wear flexibility so that you can pack less and experience more.

How to enter:
Post your submission on @instagram 
tell us about it in the caption,  tag 
@august_society #asvirtualvacation 
Register at http://augustsociety.com/contest to make sure we don’t overlook your submission! (You must be registered to win!) Contest ends on 30 June at 11:59pm SGT
Winners will be notified by email and announced on AS IG page on the 1st July

Check by tmr to see what we do at Hawaii beach!
